main event: A bright, round, white object was seen through a window, emitting a red-orange glow and a hum. The object then moved slowly, became stationary, and then moved up and disappeared to the south.
interesting points: The witness heard a hum coming from the object.
The object lit up with a bright light before disappearing to the south.
The object was described as looking like an automobile, only longer.
The witness did not go to the other room to get a better look at the object.
The report includes multiple sightings of similar unidentified objects in the area.
